REMOTE DESKTOP PROTOCOL(RDP)
 listens by default on port 3389
  Uses a client server architecture

  Windows-to-Windows 
  --target pc should allow remote desktop connection
  --we use e remote desktop connection tool
  Linux-to-Windows
  --we use xfreerdp
  xfreerdp /v:target ip /u:username /p:pass



  
